{"title":"村庄的夜","authors":["廖志理"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":10,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"村庄的夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廖志理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在夜晚每棵玉米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都像一个调皮的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墨绿的玉米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包藏了所有的珠玉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些星斗的拾掇者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉默着伫立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有温柔的须子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流露出丰收的讯息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽大的叶片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇动更加宽大的夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细细的根茎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿透了夜色的沉默"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些纯朴的孩子呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀抱着秋天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曙光般的红缨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮千年的家园……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}